---
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-6">The three pillars of local dominance</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        We don't do confusing monthly reports or vanity metrics. We focus on the three things that actually make your phone ring.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-10 border-t border-stone-300/80 pt-10 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12">
      <!-- Pillar 1 -->
      <div class="md:border-r md:border-stone-300/70 md:pr-8">
        <div class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">01</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Show up first when locals search for your service.</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          When someone searches "[your service] near me," Google shows 3 businesses on the map. If you're not in those top 3, you're invisible. We get you there and keep you there.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Full Google Business Profile optimisation
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            50+ directory listings
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Ongoing Maps ranking management
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 2 -->
      <div class="md:border-r md:border-stone-300/70 md:px-4 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Your business on Page 1 — not your competitors.</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Organic traffic that comes to you every day without spending a cent on ads. We make sure your website ranks for the exact services you offer in the areas you serve.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            SEO-optimised pages targeting buyer keywords
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Technical website fixes for speed and structure
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Suburb expansion as your rankings grow
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 3 -->
      <div class="md:pl-0 lg:pl-4">
        <div class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">03</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Build a wall of 5-star reviews automatically.</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          More reviews means more trust means more calls. You become the obvious choice before anyone even picks up the phone. We automate the whole process.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Automated review requests after every job
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Private feedback form for unhappy customers
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Professional responses to every review
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <a
        href="#book-call"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium rounded-full text-white bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Book a Free Strategy Session
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
